        "text_WMMMVe": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Postpartum is a time when the body needs warmth, steady nourishment, and care.</p><p>At for her. by Arisa, we believe food plays a foundational role in supporting recovery after birth.</p><p>Our soups are inspired by Yakuzen (薬膳), a Japanese culinary philosophy that blends principles of Traditional Chinese Medicine with seasonal Japanese ingredients. Rooted in balance and digestibility, this approach values thoughtful preparation and nourishment through everyday food.</p><p>We apply these principles to postpartum care, creating soups that are comforting, gentle, and easy to receive when energy is low.</p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        },
        "button_YyYD3L": {
